{"tid":852420,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰與工會達成協議　空中服務員退休年齡延至60歲","createTime":"2018-10-08T00:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T05:30:15.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1db5adf19a0583d0811b210fafa2b2b531861c97","tid":852420,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201810/17855625_1422537297809433_4560354148746845681_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201810%2F17855625_1422537297809433_4560354148746845681_o.jpg&h=7e770632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰航空與工會達成共識，將空中服務員的退休年齡，由現時的55歲延長至60歲，相關協議將於明年元旦日生效。<br />\n<br />\n 國泰空中服務員工會於社交網站表示，經過19個月的談判之後，終於與資方就延長退休年齡達成共識，雖然協議未盡人意，但認為是消除香港航空業年齡歧視的重大突破。<br />\n<br />\n根據協議，員工如在明年踏入55歲，可申請延長退休，並需接受面試及審批，不過最後只有不多於75%申請人獲批續約5年，惟需減薪3%至9%不等。至於舊制72小時月薪制合約的空中服務員，則全部無得留低。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-05-2018/48519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-05-2018%2F48519&d=VZw3MJ3HFo%2B70rSU20z6mm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bc065e3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-05-2018/48519</a>"},{"pid":"f27e71bb651d9a5e4cdd783bef42946486ff54c3","tid":852420,"uid":38041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:59:39.000Z","msg":"空婆空爺"},{"pid":"4fe0fcad67f66b51c5e609c759cd064c0e557dd6","tid":852420,"uid":138259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"好人好姐做呢d工做到退休....最衰過攞綜緩"},{"pid":"723a7c14c553a0a4159b35fec046457564a0342c","tid":852420,"uid":161731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"老雞是冇人要的"},{"pid":"fbfbcbcd0b6982e8f942dd2b15e08b9fab7de61e","tid":852420,"uid":44309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"屌，我唔想見到個起過35嘅空姐呀。<img src=\"/as